Text:
I notice two things strange for a wonder woman comic cover:

1: Guns (weird)

2: For the first time ever, she has realistic feminine proportions (you can actually fit organs within that waistline).

What is going on!?
thank you thank you thank you :)
MrD:You should check this series out,they made WW actually cool and that's coming from me and I never liked/cared for her character that much...

It's definitely a different take on Wonder Woman. Doesn't always hit the mark, but surprising and interesting in other ways too.

And thanks for the ul!
